ng all the available dev and static packages in alpine:\n```\napk add build-base clang openssl-dev nghttp2-dev nghttp2-static libssh2-dev libssh2-static perl \\\n    libpsl-dev libpsl-static libunistring-dev libunistring-static libidn2-dev libidn2-static \\\n    brotli-dev brotli-static zstd-dev zstd-static openssl-libs-static zlib-static \n```\n\n@vszakats Ah, yeah. I figured it might be a limitation of autotools.\nI was wondering if there might be a way to simply add a check for `-lbrotlicommon` that happens before the `-lbrotlidec` (if `-with-brotli`) since it seems that the `LIBS` value keeps getting appended to.","author_association":"NONE","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/curl/curl/issues/comments/2993064628/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"cpboyd","id":6323077,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjYzMjMwNzc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/6323077?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/cpboyd","html_url":"https://github.com/cpboyd","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cpboyd/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cpboyd/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cpboyd/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cpboyd/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cpboyd/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cpboyd/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cpboyd/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cpboyd/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cpboyd/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"id":18254372611,"node_id":"MEE_lADOAAiu0c68dvAhzwAAAARAC58D","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/curl/curl/issues/events/18254372611","actor":{"login":"bagder","id":177011,"node_id":"